reviewText: I received this product timely, in good order and for a okay price.  It was a much older version than I was expecting.  It was done in the early 80's, but it works.

I rented this video about 9 years ago and it worked wonders for me. I followed Wendy's advice and watched the inches melt away. Her simple exercises were not difficult to follow or keep up with. I would really like to have this item for my home collection and hope to locate a copy.
